    <item>
      <title>Profiling memory of C&#43;&#43; programs using Massif</title>
      <link>https://vaclavblazej.github.io/post/2021/memory_profiling/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vaclavblazej.github.io/post/2021/memory_profiling/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;valgrind&lt;/code&gt; program has many additional tools, one of which is called &lt;code&gt;massif&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.valgrind.org/docs/manual/ms-manual.html&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;manual here&lt;span style=&#34;white-space: nowrap;&#34;&gt;&amp;thinsp;↗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;).&#xA;We can call it using syntax similar to normal valgrind call.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;valgrind --tool&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;massif ./a.out &amp;lt;input.txt&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The command produces a file called &lt;code&gt;massif.out.&amp;lt;number&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; where the number is bigger for later measurements.&#xA;This file can be visualized with &lt;code&gt;massif-visualizer&lt;/code&gt; from &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/KDE/massif-visualizer&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;https://github.com/KDE/massif-visualizer&lt;span style=&#34;white-space: nowrap;&#34;&gt;&amp;thinsp;↗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;massif-visualizer massif.out.&amp;lt;number&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./img/1.png&#34; alt=&#34;massif default measurement&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;valgrind --tool&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;massif --detailed-freq&lt;span style=&#34;color:#000;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#099&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; ./a.out &amp;lt;input.txt&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./img/2.png&#34; alt=&#34;massif more frequent detail measurement&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
